The Bitcoin Treasure Hunt - for PuZZLAS!

Pst. Psssst.. .. Listen up, fellow Puzzla! There is some Bitcoin to be found on the address 3PuZZLASx9mVAw7kRhjvQd9xYCscMoPaSV!

It may be yours! So, your task is to hack away on this quest here until you have found the corresponding private key to the given Bitcoin address, before anyone else finds it! Then, make sure to send the Bitcoin to a new address of yours, so the next guy who finds the private key cannot steal the money from you!

You don't really need to have a lot of Bitcoin knowledge to solve this quest. In fact, everything you need is provided by the BIP39 tool (caution, the given address is a 'BIP49' address, so make sure to use the correct tab!). On the other, you DO need to have some IT knowledge. Without that .. well, don't even try.

Asking me questions won't give you any advantage over the other treasure seekers. If I decide to answer a question, I'll answer it publicly, so everybody learns from it.

While it is possible to claim the Bitcoin without ever communicating with me or anybody else, I'd still be happy to hear from you in case you were the one to nail this quest.

Good luck!
- Gabriel
